         <div type="translation">
            <ab>	Year 35, Tybi 4. Notification to Zenon. Sesame has been lost by night
from the grain bin; and it was ground by hand. For that reason I am unable
to measure it out and see what was lost until you yourself see it and it may
be measured out in your presence.
</ab>
